              <tr><td><strong>Enterprise</strong></td><td>Custom</td><td>Unlimited</td><td>Agency-tier</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p>$3.30 per published article at Standard utilization. Strong unit economics. The trial watermark on articles published during the $1 trial means you'll want to delete or re-publish those pieces after subscribing.</p>

        <h3>The real monthly cost for local service businesses</h3>

